# HISTORY
# 

# A client with a drawing area will appear. The shell
#  should contain a 4x4 matrix of ArrowButtonGadgets.

CompareVisual drawarea
Continue

# The bottom right arrow should start growing and moving
#  down to the right. 

# Move the cursor into the bottom right arrow. The arrow
#  highlight border should display. 

CompareVisual drawarea
LocatePointer arrowButtonGadget16
CompareVisual arrowButtonGadget16

# Iconify and Normalize the client window. 

WindowIconify Shell1
WindowDeiconify Shell1
CompareVisual drawarea

Exit
